{"tid":2009923,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港就係一個地方大部分人會將白蘭樹下當係香港產去捧去看待","createTime":"2020-05-10T06:01:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-10T11:35:52.000Z","uid":106326,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d92427f5a9e2d9b6df1623053688f84da282a919","tid":2009923,"uid":106326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:01:54.000Z","msg":"賣到七百幾蚊 又唔係本地生產<br />\n初頭寄啲料去荷蘭整<br />\n依家賣咁多樽都唔知一早超越晒香港白蘭花既產量未 隨時連白蘭花都未必係港產<br />\n個個不問是非就捧紅佢 當係香港第一枝酒<br />\n<br />\n其他兩間辛辛苦苦係香港真係拎左蒸餾廠牌既就無人理<br />\n兩枝都係賣$500 平成兩舊<br />\n真係想知七百蚊係點定價<br />\n仲有幾間都係外國蒸餾完再入口<br />\n有間無牌但有蒸籠器 未知係咪真<br />\n全部都唔開名啦費事又話咩打手<br />\n但香港個生態就係咁<br />\n認真做野唔講大話既就無人理<br />\n白蘭樹下呢啲撚屌野玩marketing 誤導消費者就被人當係香港第一瓶<br />\n都未撚講好唔好飲 值唔值呢個價<br />\n700蚊？ 我是旦揀一個國家既Gin 都買到啦"},{"pid":"a31a746db93c99e719accfdd87cfc6b6b18c6cf9","tid":2009923,"uid":1275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"另外個兩支賣500嘅係邊兩支"},{"pid":"eaf690dfb7cc28669d584fe5b2ecedede3b8ce46","tid":2009923,"uid":106326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a31a746db93c99e719accfdd87cfc6b6b18c6cf9","tid":2009923,"uid":1275,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:18:29.000Z","msg":"另外個兩支賣500嘅係邊兩支"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:24:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.lifestyleasia.com/hk/food-drink/drinks/all-you-need-to-know-about-hong-kong-gins/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lifestyleasia.com%2Fhk%2Ffood-drink%2Fdrinks%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-hong-kong-gins%2F&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=dd0f6b28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.lifestyleasia.com/hk/food-drink/drinks/all-you-need-to-know-about-hong-kong-gins/</a><br />\n<br />\n頭兩枝 寫到明hong kong distilled"},{"pid":"d431f3270f7ec488df8f2d6fa97182522522e085","tid":2009923,"uid":277533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T06:24:54.000Z","msg":"two moon<br />\n無名氏"},{"pid":"